reviewText: great dvd despite the mislabeling of the songs

Troy is A great  Artist.  If you don't have any of  Troys projects , you have really missed A great treat. Troy have  some beautiful daughters.  They can really. Sing . I have four brothers and at one time we sang as A group . My baby brother  Bishop J . C . Tidwell is still singing and his latest project is currently being sold on Amazon.

I love this wonderful spiritual group.  However, the information on the dvd was not the same as the actual songs that were viewed.  The group did a magnificent job of delivering the Word of God, just not with the songs expected on the cover.
IF YOU LIKE PRAISE,AND WORSHIP YOU WILL LOVE THIS GROUP ON THIS DVD!!!!!!!!!!! Troy Ramey & the Soul Searchers: Earth Has No Sorrow

As the customer above has already said, the songs listed on the cover are not the songs on the DVD! Because my mom is a fan of this group, I brought it for her, but she was not at all happy knowing, that there were different songs on this DVD! Not good, not good at all!
The distributor did not label this DVD correctly. The songs listed on the cover are NOT the songs on the DVD! Buyer Beware. I sent for a replacement and it is the same as the first one.
